In order to view the search results, you usually do not need to do anything because the results are already displayed on the screen. However, if you want to see results that are not fully displayed on the screen, you can use the scroll wheel to scroll down the page. In this case, suppose we need to scroll down to see more results, we can use the following actions:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "scroll_down", "scroll_repeat": 10}
]
```Please adjust to your needs ` scroll_ The value of repeat 'to scroll the appropriate amount of pages.
